OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771883654
OL,3,CGirl who died in fire at Chinese
OL,4,Ctakeaway 'much valued member of
OL,5,Ccommunity'
OL,7,FThe former school of a girl who died
OL,8,Fin a fire at a Chinese takeaway in
OL,9,FManby along with her father, have paid
OL,10,Ftribute to her.
OL,12,FYu Li, 45, and his 11-year-old
OL,13,Fdaughter, Sophie, died in the blaze at
OL,14,Fthe Golden Phoenix on Manby
OL,15,FMiddlegate, Grimoldby, near Louth,
OL,16,FLincolnshire, at 6.10am on Wednesday.
OL,18,FIn a statement, King Edward VI Grammar
OL,19,FSchool described Sophie as "polite,
OL,20,Fhardworking and thoughtful".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
