PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771883654
OL,3,CGirl who died in fire at Chinese
OL,4,Ctakeaway 'much valued member of
OL,5,Ccommunity'
OL,7,F"It is with profound sadness that we
OL,8,Fconfirm the death of one of our Year 7
OL,9,Fstudents, Sophie Li, who tragically
OL,10,Flost her life in the recent fire in
OL,11,FManby during the half-term break.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771883654
OL,3,CGirl who died in fire at Chinese
OL,4,Ctakeaway 'much valued member of
OL,5,Ccommunity'
OL,7,F"Sophie was a much-valued member of
OL,8,Four school community. She was known by
OL,9,Fstaff as a polite, hardworking and
OL,10,Fthoughtful student who approached her
OL,11,Flearning with quiet determination and
OL,12,Fmaturity beyond her years. Those who
OL,13,Ftaught her describe her as an absolute
OL,14,Fpleasure to teach and a young person
OL,15,Fdestined for great things. Her loss is
OL,16,Fdeeply felt across our school.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with Sophie's family
OL,19,Fand all those who knew and loved her
OL,20,Fat this incredibly difficult time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771883654
OL,3,CGirl who died in fire at Chinese
OL,4,Ctakeaway 'much valued member of
OL,5,Ccommunity'
OL,7,F"Since learning of the tragedy, we
OL,8,Fhave been focused on supporting our
OL,9,Fstudents, staff and the wider school
OL,10,Fcommunity. Specialist pastoral and
OL,11,Fwelfare support is available in
OL,12,Fschool, and we are working closely
OL,13,Fwith appropriate agencies to ensure
OL,14,Fthat help is in place where needed. We
OL,15,Fare particularly mindful of those
OL,16,Fstudents who may have been directly
OL,17,Faffected by the incident or who live
OL,18,Fwithin the local community.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771883654
OL,3,CGirl who died in fire at Chinese
OL,4,Ctakeaway 'much valued member of
OL,5,Ccommunity'
OL,7,F"As a school community, we will
OL,8,Fcontinue to remember Sophie with
OL,9,Fwarmth and affection. She will always
OL,10,Fremain part of the King Edward VI
OL,11,FGrammar School family."
OL,13,FLincolnshire Police said five other
OL,14,Fpeople were taken to hospital,
OL,15,Fincluding a woman in her 30s who was
OL,16,Fin a serious condition.
OL,18,FThe incident is believed to have been
OL,19,Fcaused by an air fryer and is not
OL,20,Fbeing treated as suspicious.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
